Conclusion

This project successfully analyzed unemployment trends in India using Python. The study demonstrated the significant impact of COVID-19 on employment across different states and regions. Through data cleaning, exploratory analysis, visualization, and trend identification, valuable insights were generated regarding unemployment patterns and labor market behavior.

